  <brief_title>Safety and Performance of BonyPid-1000™ in the Treatment of Gustilo IIIA and IIIB Tibial Open Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Performance of BonyPid-1000™ in the Treatment of Gustilo IIIA and IIIB Tibial Open Fractures</official_title>
