  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, multi-national, multicenter, randomized, two arms, single blind,
      Standard of Care (SOC) controlled, with blinded central reading center study. This study
      will assess the safety and performance of BonyPid-1000™ in severe open tibial fractures
      (Gustilo IIIA and IIIB) when implanted as adjunct to SOC and compared to SOC alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
